messageBody:
I am the creator of QSJ Block. I must tell you that
this is my one and only font creation, and the project
still has major flaws.
I'm not sure I have any information you need, but
ask away.

--- Robin Franzen <robee_771@...> wrote:
>  I would very much get intouch with people who have
> designed fonts using this alphabet.


===========
Never insult anyone by accident.
- Robert A. Heinlein
